// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5682 — Mass File Rename (ransomhub)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 100f3b18-0940-5841-a252-42fa78807483

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
